lab.android.rwth.evgenijandkate.plugscontrolclient.model

Interface IListItem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PlugItem

    public interface IListItem
extends java.io.Serializable
    Created by ekaterina on 04.06.2015. An interface for generalizing the list view adapter's item. The collection of this type is then used in the PlugsListAdapter.java.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      int getListItemId()
      Returns the id of the item (for instance, an id of the plug)
      java.lang.String getListItemLabel()
      Returns the label which will be shown in the adapter's list view.
      StateEnum getState()
      Returns the state of the item to be displayed with the switch (both the user with administrative rights and the user with the limited rights can change the state of an item).
      boolean isChecked()
      Returns this item's ischecked flag to be used in the list view for the state of a combo box
